title: GTA+
headline: GTA+
subtitle: This Month’s Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (December 10 - January 7) will also receive:

— The new Vapid FMJ MK V (Super)
— A GTA$1,000,000 discount on new Prix Luxury Mansion properties
— A free upgrade to the Mansion Vehicle Workshop
— The Santa Skull Sweater and Santa Skull Track Pants
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
